projects.name: Data Science Program in Finlatics
projects.description: Analyzed YouTube top creators dataset to uncover trends in subscribers, channel categories, and geographical distributions. Identified key patterns to inform content strategy and optimize channel performance. Provided data-driven insights for targeted content creation and marketing efforts.

projects.name: Food Delivery App
projects.description: Developed a cutting-edge food delivery platform using React, NodeJS, and MongoDB. Integrated Stripe for seamless payments and incorporated personalized recommendations. Aimed to enhance user experience and redefine industry standards.

projects.name: Student Report Management System
projects.description: Developed a console-based application for managing student information. Features include storing records, sorting by name, finding the student with the minimum marks, and searching for contact details by first name or roll number.

projects.name: Comparative Analysis of Stroke Risk Prediction Methods
projects.description: Developed a system to predict stroke risk using machine and deep learning algorithms, including Random Forest and Multi-Layer Perceptron. Achieved performance metrics like accuracy, precision, recall, and F1-score, with results compared through graphical analysis.

experiences.description: Analyzing Digital Indias Impact on Healthcare Reach and Socio-Economic Factors Analyzed how Digital India has enhanced healthcare accessibility, efficiency, and quality through technology integration (EHRs, telemedicine, mobile apps). Evaluated challenges and opportunities, and assessed effects on patient outcomes and healthcare delivery. Findings support informed decision-making for healthcare improvement in India.
